thread.title: Muscat Securities Market Gains 87 Points

author: Saudi Press Agency
title: Muscat Securities Market Gains 87 Points
text:
(MENAFN - Saudi Press Agency) Muscat Dhu-AlQa'dah 15 1436 August 30 2015 SPA -- Muscat Securities Market (MSM) general index (30) today added (87.6) points comprising a rise by (1.51%) to close at (5904.44) points compared to the last session which stood at (5816.80) points. 

The trading value today stood at (RO 4.28 million) comprising a rise by (0.39%) compared to the last session which stood at (RO 4.26) million. 

The report released by MSM pointed out that the market value rose by (0.21%) to reach about (RO 14.70) billion. 
--SPA 
14:42 LOCAL TIME 11:42 GMT
